section.section:
Of the nine members of the Board of Directors:
two shall be nominated by the American Insurance Association;
two shall be nominated by the Property Casualty Insurers Association of America;
one shall be associated with a domestic insurer that is not affiliated with a group listed in item (i) or (ii) of this paragraph;
two may not be affiliated with a member company of a group listed in item (i) or (ii) of this paragraph or with a domestic insurer that is otherwise represented on the Board of Directors; and
two shall be nominated by the members of the Board of Directors selected under items (i) through (iv) of this paragraph.
